<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٨١٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5614">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ زِيَادٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ </a>: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«الْوَلَدُ لِلْفِرَاشِ وَلِلْعَاهِرِ الْحَجَرُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>